Name.Display: Dell SupportAssist OS Recovery Plugin for Dell Update

Description.Display: The Dell Update - SupportAssist Update Plugin works in conjunction with the Dell Update application to keep your systems recovery environment up to date with the latest version of SupportAssist OS Recovery. SupportAssist OS Recovery is a powerful recovery tool designed to help you diagnosis, fix or recover your system when you are experiencing issues. The operating system will provide you a kiosk-style application for easy interaction that will guide you through various options to correct your systems issue. This operating system will automatically engage on system boot failures. In addition, SupportAssist OS Recovery can be selected manually during boot by pressing F12 to call the one time boot and choosing the "SupporAssist OS Recovery" option.
